    • beginning

      public static void beginning​(double _g, double _m, double _mu, double _vmax, double _tol, Vector2d _start, Vector2d _goal, java.lang.String _height, int _version, @NotNull @NotNull java.util.ArrayList<Vector2d> _treePositions, java.util.ArrayList<Vector2d> _sandPositions, java.lang.String _heightMap, java.util.ArrayList<Tree> _stumps) throws java.io.IOException
      set all variables for terrain and physics engine
      Parameters:
      _g - double, gravitation force
      _m - double, mass of ball
      _mu - double, friction coefficients
      _vmax - double, maximum speed for golf ball
      _tol - double, radius around hole that golf ball has to eventually land in
      _start - Vector2d, starting position for golf ball
      _goal - Vector2d, position of hole
      _height - String, function to calculate height for terrein
      _version - int, determines manual of filereader for input
      _treePositions - ArrayList, list of positions of trees
      _sandPositions - ArrayList, list of position of sand spaces
      _heightMap - String, name of file with heightmap to describe terrain
      _stumps - ArrayList, list of stumps for maze
      Throws:
      java.io.IOException - if one or more parameters are empty
